    LLMController -->|creates| InferenceModel["InferenceModel"]
    LLMController -->|creates| LLMHTTPRoute["HTTPRoute"]
    LLMController -->|creates| DestRule["DestinationRule"]
    LLMController -->|deploys| Scheduler

    %% External dependencies
    ISController -->|depends on| Istio["Istio Service Mesh"]
    ISController -->|depends on| Knative["Knative Serving"]
    LLMController -->|depends on| GatewayAPI["Gateway API"]
    LLMController -->|depends on| GWIE["Gateway API<br/>Inference Extension"]
    LLMController -->|depends on| LWSOperator["LeaderWorkerSet<br/>Operator"]

    %% Internal integrations
    ISController -.->|integrates| ODHModelCtrl["odh-model-controller"]
    ISController -.->|deployed by| RHODSOperator["rhods-operator"]

    %% Storage
    StorageInit -->|downloads from| S3["S3 / GCS / Azure<br/>Object Storage"]

